title: AutoBoss Snow Trunk Shovel
description: When you are out and about this winter, don't be caught in inclement weather unprepared. The True Temper AutoBoss is a portable shovel that clears snow from hard to reach places like around tires and in between parked cars. It offers simple extension and retraction, multiple hand placement options, a knob for adjusting the angle of the blade and its sleek, compact profile makes for easy storage. In fact, it's so lightweight and portable that you'll want to take it along with you whether youâ€™re going hiking, camping or just commuting to work.
